{"tid":1614924,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港警實彈對付示威者 英國50議員聯署斥中國違國際法 敦促外相清楚指出中國明顯違反《聯合聲明》","createTime":"2019-10-03T02:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T06:06:31.000Z","uid":70063,"like":91,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"c69a4da24e7df32bb734b67eab88f30a3a46fca2","tid":1614924,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:39:55.000Z","msg":"港警周二向18歲示威學生近距離開槍，震驚全球。在英國，包括前外相聶偉敬（Sir Malcolm Rifkind）在內的50名國會議員周三發表聯合聲明，譴責中國在處理香港問題上違反國際法。<br />\n<br />\n這份由非政府組織「Fight for Freedom: Stand with Hong Kong」負責協調的跨黨派聲明，敦促外相藍韜文（Dominic Raab）發表清楚聲明，指出中國明顯違反《中英聯合聲明》條款。<br />\n<br />\n有份聯署的自民黨黨鞭兼國會議員卡邁克爾（Alistair Carmichael）說：「中國在香港殘暴壓制人權，港警甚至以實彈對付示威者，由此可見，中國違反了國際法。單是向中國提出有關問題並不足夠，我呼籲外相準備一系列經濟和政府措施，確保香港人（包括英國護照持有人）的自由和基本權利（包括普選權）得到維護。我呼籲各方克制，譴責各方暴力。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191003/60111130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191003%2F60111130&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7M3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=713f2d3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191003%2F60111130&h=ebd1cde2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191003/60111130</a>"},{"pid":"831f10d80bed949e6bf137a520c03f655c2023b7","tid":1614924,"uid":41005,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:40:27.000Z","msg":"英國佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731fc7f2b6effba02cc315ebffdbe5de1944152c","tid":1614924,"uid":129924,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:41:26.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"feec684766eb16b681d85123c9af3562c75229b6","tid":1614924,"uid":233651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:42:07.000Z","msg":"鄰國口交部好似無出過聲？"},{"pid":"d5936fed071a264864b7060d